    {
      "_id": "ZIwfKBGKmADbDsgp",
      "name": "Engolir",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Teste de Resistência de Destreza: CD 25, uma criatura Agarrado by the kraken (it can have up to four creatures swallowed at a time). 23 (3d8 + 10) dano perfurante. If o alvo is Large or smaller, it is swallowed and no longer Agarrado. A swallowed creature fica com a condição Impedido, has Total Cover against attacks and other effects outside the kraken, and takes 24 (7d6) dano de ácido at the start of each of its turns.\nIf the kraken takes 50 de dano or more on a single turn from uma criatura inside it, the kraken must succeed on a CD 25 Constituição saving throw at the end of that turn or regurgitate all swallowed creatures, each of which falls in a space within 3 m of the kraken with a condição Caído. If the kraken dies, any swallowed creature no longer fica com a condição Impedido and can escape from the corpse using 4,5 m of movement, exiting Caído.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
